🇪🇸 2026 Spanish Autónomo Tax Calculator
A lightweight, browser-based estimation tool for freelancers (Autónomos) in Spain. This calculator helps you estimate your monthly net income by accounting for 2026 Social Security (Seguridad Social) brackets, IRPF (income tax) retention, and startup reductions.

