Features
SS Bracket Selection: Includes the 15 tiers for 2026 Social Security contributions.

Tarifa Plana Mode: Toggle for first-year flat rate Social Security.

IRPF Reductions: Toggle for the 20% startup tax reduction (first 2 years).

Regional Tax Variations: Selectable regional IRPF brackets to account for local tax differences (e.g., Madrid vs. Catalunya).

Real-time Breakdown: Detailed visualization of yearly vs. monthly contributions.

How to use
This tool is a standalone HTML file.

Directly in Browser: You can simply open the index.html file in any modern web browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari).

Host on GitHub Pages:

Enable GitHub Pages in your repository settings (under Settings > Pages).

Set the branch to main (or master).

Your calculator will be live at [https://your-username.github.io/your-repo-name/](https://your-username.github.io/your-repo-name/).

